===Pronunciation===

ἅγιος / hagios / hag'-ee-os

From ἅγος hagos (an awful thing) compare G53, [H2282]; sacred (physically pure, morally blameless or religious, ceremonially consecrated): 
===[[Adjective]]===
(most) [[holy]] (one, thing), [[saint]].